Package eu.wauz.wauzstarter

This package contains everything, that needs to be done before WauzCore starts.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EmptyWorldCreator
    Represents various types of options that may be used to create an empty world.
    SeasonalSurvivalManager
    This class is used to create a new world when a Survival season starts.
    SeasonalSurvivalUtils
    An util class to spawn structures in seasonal Survival worlds.
    WauzRestartScheduler
    The restart scheduler schedules restarts.
    WauzStarter
    The main class of this module, used to setup the environment for WauzCore.
